### Test Image Upload Endpoint
# NOTE: Replace "path/to/your/image.jpg" with a real file path on your computer.
POST http://localhost:4000/analysis/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="path/to/your/image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< E:\download.jpg

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--
